isOwner().return: true if `msg.sender` is the owner of the contract.

price(string,uint256,uint256).details: Returns the price to register or renew a name.

params.duration: How long the name is being registered or extended for, in seconds.
params.name: The name being registered or renewed.

price(string,uint256,uint256).return: The price of this renewal or registration, in wei.

renounceOwnership().details: Allows the current owner to relinquish control of the contract.

params._usdOracle: The address of the price oracle to use.

params._rentPrices: The price array. Each element corresponds to a specific                   name length; names longer than the length of the array                   default to the price of the last element.

transferOwnership(address).details: Allows the current owner to transfer control of the contract to a newOwner.

params.newOwner: The address to transfer ownership to.

renounceOwnership().notice: Renouncing to ownership will leave the contract without an owner. It will not be possible to call the functions with the `onlyOwner` modifier anymore.
